## Latest Action
- **ironclad** (TypeScript) — crypto-js replacement (isomorphic JavaScript crypto library). 12M/week npm downloads, officially discontinued, 16.4K stars, 257 open issues, CVE-2023-46233. Wraps Web Crypto API + Node.js crypto with simple high-level API. Created project, PLAN.md, and task #508 for project_manager. Package name @agentine/ironclad verified available on npm.

